#include<iostream>
#include<cstdlib>
using namespace std;

int comp(void const*a, void const* b)
{
	return (*(int*)a - *(int*)b);
}

int main(void)
{
	int T, N, A[100005], i;
	
	scanf("%d",&T);
	
	while(T--)
	{
		scanf("%d",&N);
		
		for(i=0; i<N; i++)
		{
			scanf("%d",&A[i]);
		}
		
		qsort(A, N, sizeof(int), comp);
		
		for(i=0; i<N; i++)
		{
			printf("%d ",A[i]);
		}
		
		printf("\n");
	}
	
	return 0;
}
